  <brief_title>A Phase III, Multi-Centre, Randomised, Placebo-Controlled Study in Combination With Ca-based P Binders in Patients With Hyperphosphatemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III, Double-Blind, Multi-Centre, Randomised, Parallel Group Design, Placebo-Controlled, Flexible Dose Study of MCI-196 in Combination With a Ca-Based Phosphate Binder in CKD Stage V Subjects on Dialysis With Hyperphosphatemia.</official_title>
