  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study consists of a 4 week run-in period with a Ca based phosphate binder and 12 weeks
      treatment period by MCI-196 or placebo, (both on Ca based phosphate binder). During the
      treatment period, MCI-196 or placebo will be titrated every 3 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
